front.title: •Colonel Dyer
front.gametext: While at Bunker of an Endor battleground site, prevents Ominous Rumors from being canceled. Your [Endor] troopers may move as a 'react' to same site.
front.lore: Responsible for defense of control bunker. Leader. Worked closely with Moff Jerjerrod to plan the installation's defense. Instructed to hold troops in reserve.

combo: Colonel Dyer + Commander Igar + Scout Recon
